Suppliers
At BorgWarner, the establishment and maintenance of effective relationships remains a cornerstone of our business. We work closely with our suppliers to reduce waste, improve performance, and advance technology in the most competitive and creative ways. If you are a current BorgWarner supplier, we appreciate your ongoing and unwavering commitment to these shared ideals. If you are interested in becoming a supplier to BorgWarner, this portal is designed to get you on the right track.








Supplier Diversity

BorgWarner provides equal opportunities to diverse business enterprises. If you are certified minority or female owned business, please make sure and fill out the appropriate information on the registration page (link below) and the appropriate people within BorgWarner will be notified.






Supplier Code of Conduct

These beliefs, which are deeply rooted in our culture, also serve as a framework for the standards of business conduct we expect of any supplier that does business with us.






Supplier Expectations 

Our Stated vision is to increase shareholder value by procuring goods, services and materials from a supply base which endows BW with a measurable competitive edge.  









Supplier Manual 
Our business relationship will be based on the requirements outlined in our Supplier Manual, a copy of which is located in the download section of this site.




Major Commodities Purchases

Here we have a brief summary of the kinds of products and materials that we purchase within the company. This is not a complete list, as our businesses and technologies continue to grow. Browse the Product Section of the corporate web site to learn about the different products offered and markets we serve. This will help you to get a sense of how your company could support BorgWarner's global growth.




Purchase Order Terms and Conditions
Our Terms and Conditions apply to our purchase orders and the purchase orders are limited to and conditional upon supplier's acceptance of our Terms and Conditions. Any additional or different terms proposed by the supplier are unacceptable and expressly rejected. The Terms and Conditions for the particular countries are available here. The particular country's Terms and Conditions that apply to a purchase order will be determined by the country location to which the goods or services are delivered.

